br />\n【本報訊】5間宿生會去年在校園「叫莊」（Chanting）時爆衝突，一名二年級男生涉推撞兩同學，被控兩項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，案件昨提訊。由於被告將聘私人律師抗辯，案件押後再訊。主任裁判官練錦鴻得悉被告是一名學生後揶揄謂：「讀乜嘢？武術呀？」當值律師索取指示後，指被告讀電子工程系。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後准保釋<br />\n<br />\n被告莊鈞絡（20歲）被控去年2月26日在科大賽馬會大堂襲擊黎俊威及錢卓軒。控方原已準備答辯，但由當值律師代表的被告申請毋須答辯，指被告將聘私人律師代表，亦需索取文件。裁判官押後至下月10日再訊，准他以現金5,000元保釋，不得接觸證人。<br />\n資料顯示當時各學會正進行宣傳期，案發當日是5學生宿生會的「last chant」，逾百人聚集賽馬會大堂叫口號。至晚上情況混亂學生互相推撞。有學生稱遇襲，共5人送院，分別手部受傷及胸口紅腫，科大2014年亦曾發生同類事件。<br />\n案件編號：KTCC369/17<br />\n■記者戴國輝&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170225/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170225%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=60dc70bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170225/19939809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170225%2F19939809&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d554890f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170225%2F19939809&h=e8db8e61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170225/19939809</a>"},{"pid":"aaac561731693a826f867a3ff7d7894e094b5fc8","tid":158160,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1f6b86d2f08a57a274044dc37dfa767b21da51","tid":158160,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"香港大學space學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95937cba12dd5d8a2ffc751442813f4b2873e6e0","tid":158160,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"又有一堆asshole仔扮大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" c